\binom{n+1}{k}\frac{1}{(n+1)^{k}}=\Bigg(\binom{n}{k}+\binom{n}{k-1}\Bigg)\frac{1}{(n+1)^{k}} =\\ \binom{n}{k}\frac{1}{(n+1)^{k}} + \binom{n}{k-1}\frac{1}{(n+1)^{k}} \leq \frac{1}{(k)!}
